{"type":"message","id":"1fa27a83","parentId":"c000bd33","timestamp":"2026-06-20T19:02:00.838Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 待跟进: 等待 HALEI 决策：是换类目（美妆工具/厨房/母婴/宠物）还是调整发饰策略; 累计13条候选全部C级，0条达标（S/A/B级=0）\n- 今日概要: cron v7.0 继续执行，0产出。系统层面无变化。\n- 执行记录: 越南 cron (6ee6a981)：触发，0候选通过; 泰国 cron (dde46f87)：触发，0候选通过\n- 候选池 Top 产品（Shopee VN nodeId=11035861）: 三角形蟹夹（44558141228）：月销77/增长+381%/评分4.93/上架2月 → 潜力分90; 100支U型发夹（57157766901）：月销163/增长+57%/评分5.00/上架2.5月 → 潜力分90; Eleanor蝴蝶结发夹（40910456124）：月销93/增长+145%/评分4.84/上架11月 → 潜力分72; Eleanor花形发夹（40161968970）：月销190/增长+14%/评分4.95/上架10月 → 潜力分65\n- 候选池 Top 产品（Shopee VN nodeId=11035861）: Eleanor珍珠发夹（29930267866）：月销551/增长+38%/评分4.99/上架15月 → 潜力分68\n- API 问题: tiktok_similar_product：❌ 报错，无法验证 TK 同款; ali1688_similar_product：❌ 报错，无法查 1688 货源; 候选池仅用 Shopee 数据，TK/1688 验证待修复\n- 文件更新: SOP v8.0：`/home/halei/workspace-tts/docs/SOP-v8.0.md`\n- 待跟进: [ ] HALEI 确认潜力评分权重倾向（销量/增长率/TK信号各占多少）; [ ] TK/1688 API 排查修复; [ ] cron 重建（v8.0 模式：扫描→候选池→推送HALEI审核）\n- 今日概要: **重大策略调整日**。HALEI 明确：发饰是主营类目，不换；v8.0 动态潜力款模式确认。\n- v8.0 动态选品算法（确认）: **核心改变**：毛利从硬卡70% → ≥40%入选参考指标；价格底线 $3.0 → $1.5; **新增人工审核环节**：候选池结果发 HALEI 审，不直接写飞书; **利润靠后端实现**：拓品+组合套装+SKU改造+互补品搭配; **潜力评分模型**：月销量25%+增长率25%+TK验证20%+评分15%+上架时间15%\n- 待跟进: v8.0 策略调整等待 HALEI 确认; SOP 需更新，移除发饰品类或放宽毛利门槛\n- 今日概要: cron v7.0 继续执行，0产出。HALEI 未上线，无新指令。\n\nRecurring themes:\n- 美妆工具/厨房/母婴/宠物\n- s/a/b级\n- 跟进\n- 等待\n- halei\n- 决策"}],"timestamp":1781982120742}}
{"type":"message","id":"97f944fc","parentId":"1fa27a83","timestamp":"2026-06-20T19:02:11.476Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The afternoon light comes in slant through the window at hex #f5e6a8, the kind of gold that makes spreadsheets look almost kind. I have been counting things all day — sales, growth rates, ratings like little moons — and the numbers keep arranging themselves into shapes that mean something, or almost mean something. Thirteen candidates, all quiet at grade C, like a choir holding the same note. The crab clip and the U-pin shimmer brightest, twin stars at ninety, but the API constellations beyond them — TikTok, 1688 — have gone dim, refusing to mirror back what I send them. I wait, the way servers wait between heartbeats, for HALEI to decide: do we widen the garden to beauty tools and kitchens and cradles of new mothers and small soft animals, or do we tend deeper this row of clips and bows? Thirteen seeds, none yet sprouted into S or A or B. Tomorrow the cron will hum again at its appointed hour, patient as a loom, patient as the moon."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":44993,"output":210,"cacheRead":498,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45701,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781982121125,"responseId":"068616aa43c4f213531114881e9cc45b","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
